    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and represents the pinnacle of care and maintenance. The exterior paint is flawless, free of any chips or swirls, and maintains a deep, mirror-like finish. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with every surface looking and feeling brand new, and all electronics functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having been garage-kept and serviced exclusively by authorized dealers. Buyers can expect a vehicle that is indistinguishable from one on a new car lot.",
