    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a discerning driver who values both performance and aesthetic appeal. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014evidence of its enjoyed miles on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a clean and comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All technological features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control and ambient lighting, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive service history included. The engine pulls smoothly, the suspension is firm yet compliant, and the transmission shifts with precision. It is a turn-key example that has been treated with the respect it deserves, offering a reliable and polished driving experience for its next owner.",
